<p>Schema.org releases new vocabulary types regularly. AI-specific types are on the roadmap. Watch for types that define content provenance, factual accuracy signals, and AI licensing permissions.</p>
<h3>The Knowledge Graph Advantage Compounds</h3>
<p>Every page you add with connected schema markup strengthens your site's knowledge graph. This is the Content Compound Effect in action. Three months of consistent schema implementation builds an entity graph that AI systems recognize and trust.</p>
